entries.femaleVariant: Calling all NCPD subcons. APB out on suspected organized crime activity over on Sycamore Street.
Due to nonpayment of rent and related fees, Night City has terminated its lease agreement with Impala Automatics for industrial property owned by the city.
City authorities have offered a reward for the successful eviction of Impala Automatics.
Impala Automatics has failed to comply with the decision and now illegally occupies the premises specified in the contract.
